name: Inspirefest 2016
blurb:
![Inspirefest 2016](http://i.minus.com/iAGugZP2EkVtP.png)

Inspirefest 2016 is a two day international event that connects professionals interested in the future of science, technology, engineering, and mathematics with new perspectives on innovation, leadership and success. Plus unique networking at our exciting Fringe Festival taking place from 30 June - 2 July, 2016.
